CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1960, pg. B7 reads: "11. Lester E. Cauffiel and Charles Brinkman display a dazzling eye-pleasing mantelpiece complete with television for the Artcraft Mantel Company."
TitMainTitle: Lester E. Cauffiel and Charles Brinkman standing in Artcraft Mantel Company booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
